[Mowgli] Shere Khan has brought us
nothing but chaos.

01:23:03.436 --> 01:23:05.436
[wolves whining]

01:23:11.486 --> 01:23:13.736
[Mowgli] Akela, we must kill the tiger.

01:23:15.865 --> 01:23:17.615
